content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 502.3 - Rules to be printed on application form

State Regulations

Such rules and regulations shall either be printed on the
service application form or shall be printed on a folder which shall be
delivered to every applicant for service. Notes
